data.meta_description: For a licensed and experienced electrician in Euclid, Ohio contact Duffy’s Electric at 440-341-7892 today for rewiring, installation, and electrical upgrades.
data.text:
When it comes to your business, an electrical issue can disrupt your day-to-day activities. With over 200 years of combined experience and 20 years of service, Duffy's Electric has a wide base of knowledge and expertise to ensure your electrical wiring is safe and adheres to all standards and codes. To request a prompt and professional electrical service in Cuyahoga County and Lake County contact Duffy’s Electric at 440-341-7892 today.

Commercial Electrical Rewiring

Duffy's Electric specializes in electrical rewiring for apartments, gas stations, restaurants, and other commercial properties. Old or damaged wiring can produce a multitude of hazards for as well as inefficient energy usage. We have the equipment and expertise to handle jobs of all sizes from single rooms to a full-property rewire.

Electrical Repairs

Electrical issues can be a major safety hazard and should be resolved as soon as possible. Our knowledgeable technicians can help and get your electric back to operating smoothly.

Explosion Proof Wiring

Duffy's Electric installs industry-grade explosion proof wiring for properties at risk for fires such as gas stations. We add a chemical proof compound to the wiring to prevent hazardous situations. We are happy to advise you on the best options and electrical design to ensure maximum safety and efficiency.
